    <measure>Characterizing the types of symptom-based and objective definitions used by sites to determine patients' response to CRT</measure>
    <time_frame>6 months</time_frame>
    <description>The types of &quot;symptom-based and objective definitions&quot; are to be determine by the data provided through this world wide registry.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
